{SOUTH has an invitational (9 point) hand with five \Ss.

She bids it in the standard way - first transfer NORTH to \Ss, then invite 
the game by bidding 2NT.

NORTH, with 17 points and three \Ss, accepts the game invitation and chooses 4\S.}

